            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The text in the genitive singular reads ‘ΑΒΙΛΛΙΟΥ’, associating the dedicand or the deceased from the monument with the Roman family name Avilius.  Related family name is recorded in the military camp at Kabyle, ca. 40 km north, see IG Bulg 3.2 1777</p>
            </div>
